## Introduction

This extension leverages the capabilities of GPT-3.5 Turbo to assist you in your software development process.

## Installation

1. Open VS Code
2. Go to the Extensions view by clicking on the Extensions icon in the Activity Bar on the side of the window.
3. Search for "GPT Code Generator" and install it.

## Usage

1. Highlight the text you want to generate code for.
2. Right-click to open the context menu and choose "Generate with GPT".

> **Important**: You will need to enter your OpenAI API key upon first use.

## Configuration

To enter or update your OpenAI API Key:

1. Go to `Settings > Extensions > GPT Code Generator`.
2. Enter your OpenAI API Key in the 'API Key' field.

